## Attribution Requirements

When using NORP specifications or implementations, please provide attribution:

**For specifications**:
"This system implements NORP-001 (NeuraScope Orchestration Reference Patterns),
licensed under CC BY 4.0. See https://norp.neurascope.ai"

**For code**:
Include the MIT License text and copyright notice in your distribution.

